key_statement.statement:
Plants not cespitose, with short, stout, horizontal rhizomes; inner band of bract
        sheaths with convex projections to 3.2 mm; scales dark brown with conspicuous white
        borders;

Tallest culms 25 – 50 cm; proximal pistillate spike bracts 1.5 – 4 times as long as
        inflorescences; peduncles of staminate spikes 0.2 – 0.5 length of staminate
        spikes;
